name: Botched By Nature
overview: They have fixed the unfixable and thought they'd seen it all. Dr. Terry Dubrow and Dr. Paul Nassif will travel across the country to change the lives of those who have been botched by genetics or traumatic incidents. This series follows the doctors' nation-wide pursuit as they seek to transform the lives of patients willing to share their powerful stories with the world, all while learning things they never thought they'd know about one another and deepening the bromance that fans have come to know and love.

episodes.name: Double Down on Ds!
episodes.overview: Paul and Terry take their surgical expertise on the road. In the series premiere, the doctors help a young woman with deformed breasts, and a twin born with facial abnormalities.

episodes.name: This Little Piggy...
episodes.overview: The doctors meet a female war veteran that was struck by lightning leaving her disfigured. Then, they help a woman who has a misplaced toe on each foot.

episodes.name: Double Trouble
episodes.overview: The Doctors travel to Iowa to see a young father whose chest implant is threatening his life, before meeting a pair of twins with matching cleft deformities who want to look more identical.

episodes.name: Crooked and Cracked
episodes.overview: The doctors head to Louisiana to meet with a man whose nasal syndrome has him tired of facing the public. In California they meet with a woman who was born with a conjoined twin.

episodes.name: The Chronicles of Hernia
episodes.overview: Doctors Dubrow and Nassif travel to Virginia to meet a young woman with severely deformed breasts. Later, Paul discovers he has a serious medical condition.

episodes.name: Boobs & Tubes
episodes.overview: The doctors meet a young mother born with Pectus Excavatum. They also consult with a woman born pre-maturely whose nasal complications grew with her into adulthood.

episodes.name: Collapsed In & Busted Out
episodes.overview: The doctors head to Arizona to help a woman whose nose collapsed into her own face. In NYC, they meet a college student with an oversized breast, and later check up on Tiffany Pollard.
